<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Studio Policies</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #000; padding: 60px 80px; background: white; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 3px solid #000; padding-bottom: 20px; }
        .document-title { font-size: 24pt; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 15px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .date { text-align: right; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #555; }
        .info-box { background: #f8f8f8; border: 2px solid #333; padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .info-box h3 { margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 5px; }
        .info-row { display: flex; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .info-label { font-weight: bold; width: 200px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .info-value { flex: 1; }
        .section { margin: 25px 0; }
        .section-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .section-content { text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        ul { margin-left: 40px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        li { margin-bottom: 5px; }
        strong { font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header"><div class="document-title">STUDIO POLICIES</div></div>
    <div class="date">Effective Date: {{date}}</div>
    <div class="info-box">
        <h3>Studio Information</h3>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Studio Name:</div><div class="info-value">{{BusinessName}}</div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Address:</div><div class="info-value">{{BusinessAddress}}</div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Contact:</div><div class="info-value">{{Email}} | {{Phone}}</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">1. CLASS BOOKING AND CANCELLATION</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>Reservations:</strong> Classes must be booked in advance through our booking system. Space is limited and available on a first-come, first-served basis.
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>Cancellations:</strong> Cancel at least 12 hours before class to avoid losing your class credit. No-shows will result in loss of credit.
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>Late Arrivals:</strong> Doors close 10 minutes after class starts. Late arrivals may be turned away to avoid disrupting class.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">2. STUDIO ETIQUETTE</div>
        <ul>
            <li>Arrive 10-15 minutes early to check in and set up</li>
            <li>Turn off or silence mobile devices</li>
            <li>Wear appropriate athletic attire and remove shoes when required</li>
            <li>Maintain personal hygiene (no strong fragrances)</li>
            <li>Clean and return all equipment after use</li>
            <li>Respect the quiet atmosphere before and after class</li>
            <li>No eating or chewing gum in the studio</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">3. HEALTH AND SAFETY</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            All participants must complete a health questionnaire and waiver before their first class. Inform instructors of any injuries, medical conditions, or pregnancy. Stop any activity that causes pain or discomfort.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">4. CHILDREN AND GUESTS</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Children are only allowed in designated areas or classes. Guests must sign a waiver and pay applicable fees. Members are responsible for their guests' behavior.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">5. PERSONAL BELONGINGS</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> is not responsible for lost, stolen, or damaged personal items. Use lockers when available and keep valuables with you.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">6. PHOTOGRAPHY AND RECORDING</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Photography, video recording, or live streaming is prohibited without prior permission. We may take photos/videos for marketing purposes - notify us if you prefer not to be photographed.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">7. CONDUCT AND RESPECT</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            We maintain a safe, welcoming environment for all. Harassment, discrimination, bullying, or disruptive behavior will not be tolerated and may result in immediate membership termination.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">8. POLICY CHANGES</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> reserves the right to modify these policies at any time. Updates will be posted on our website and in-studio.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">ACKNOWLEDGEMENT</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            By using our studio, you acknowledge that you have read and agree to follow these policies.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>